---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Design Leadership">
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="hero-tagline">Design Leadership</p>
      <h1>Human-centered organizations for human-centered products</h1>
      <p class="hero-description">
        I'm Tobias Treppmann, a hands-on design leader who builds the psychological safety,
        inclusive collaboration, and technical excellence that enables breakthrough user experiences.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="case-studies">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Case Studies</h2>
        <p class="text-muted">Recent work demonstrating hands-on leadership and technical depth</p>
      </div>

      <div class="case-studies-grid">
        <a href="/case-studies/churchdesk" class="case-study-card">
          <h3>When 'Simple Booking' Isn't Simple</h3>
          <p class="subtitle">ChurchDesk Booking System</p>
          <p>Designing a deceptively simple booking experience that masks extraordinary complexity—multi-stakeholder coordination for sensitive contexts.</p>
          <div style="margin-top: var(--space-md);">
            <span class="tag">Complex Systems</span>
            <span class="tag">Multi-stakeholder</span>
            <span class="tag">Platform Design</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/case-studies/ninox" class="case-study-card">
          <h3>Redesigning How We Work Together</h3>
          <p class="subtitle">Leadership & Inclusion</p>
          <p>When a team labels someone "difficult," the instinct is to manage the person. But what if the problem isn't the person—it's how the team works?</p>
          <div style="margin-top: var(--space-md);">
            <span class="tag">Leadership</span>
            <span class="tag">Team Design</span>
            <span class="tag">Inclusion</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/case-studies/modern-practice" class="case-study-card">
          <h3>Accelerating Design with AI</h3>
          <p class="subtitle">AI-First Design Process</p>
          <p>AI compresses the path from idea to testable prototype. Developing an AI-first design process at Bibel TV and teaching teams to do the same.</p>
          <div style="margin-top: var(--space-md);">
            <span class="tag">Claude Code</span>
            <span class="tag">Zed/VSCode</span>
            <span class="tag">AI Prototyping</span>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


</Layout>
